{"tid":2296671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國是城池做主軸　是城市文明　圍村是閩粵特色　土客、漳泉戰爭","createTime":"2020-11-22T16:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T16:17:55.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfb451381a558ce7358ee94a16b16bb45493e4b","tid":2296671,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"迪士尼真人《花木蘭》有土樓。土樓、圍村這些不只是建築物不同，更是生活形態不同。有村落聯盟，充滿戰爭，著名的有漳泉大戰、土客大戰。他們那邊是城池文明，我們這邊陸上是土樓文明、圍村文明。就像歐洲中世紀，因自然環壞關係，蠻族發展出來的是城堡，不是城池這種建築物有城市特質。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1310796695165235200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1310796695165235200&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7b75b884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1310796695165235200&h=ceeab073\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1310796695165235200</a>"}]}